About SciNotes
==============

The *SciNotes* system is a simple web-page system that allows to write notes
using the simple [*MarkDown*][mdref] format. Markdown has recently become a popular format
to structure texts and can easily be converted to HTML and other formats.



Features
--------

The features of the *SciNotes* system are an easy use (hence MarkDown), database
backed storage, versioning of notes and a special service to store experiment results
by simply uploading results in CSV file format.


[mdref]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown
